commit.message:
i386-2.C: Add -mpopcnt -mabm -mlwp to dg-options.

	* g++.dg/other/i386-2.C: Add -mpopcnt -mabm -mlwp to dg-options.
	* g++.dg/other/i386-3.C: Ditto.
	* g++.dg/other/i386-5.C: Remove duplicated test.
	* g++.dg/other/i386-6.C: Ditto.

From-SVN: r155238
